	<text>You receive a hail from a station orbiting a nearby planet. "Captain, we are Federation Terraforming Team R11 and are in need of assistance. Do you have some time?"</text>
	<text>You receive a hail from a station orbiting a nearby planet. "Captain, we are Federation Terraforming Team W8-2 and are in need of assistance. Do you have some time?"</text>
