			<removeCrew class="mantis">
				<clone>true</clone>
				<text>Fortunately, dismemberment is one of the many cases your Clone Bay readily covers. That doesn't make it hurt any less, but your crew are probably used to it by now.</text>
			</removeCrew>
		</event>
	</choice>
	<choice req="LIST_CREW_SUZERAIN" hidden="true">
