		<event>
			<text>The Engi are visibly uncomfortable in the presence of your Suzerain. It enters the room where the Mantis is kept, and in a matter of minutes has slit its throat. When it returns, it explains: "It one of brainless Free Mantis types. Only solution was kill." The Engi seem satisfied and pay you for your "efforts".</text>
